text: Þis sanden þe landimaren to Mapeldertune.
Arest of elmere up anlang streames on Winterburne on þa dich.
And þanne anlang riscemeres oþ hit cumd to þere alde dich þanne andlang diche foren ongen Wiþig þeuel þanen.
Of sex þorne on anne þorn þinel with Winterburne.
And þanne andland Winterburne on anne water pet.
On grenenhille of þa hege reawe onlang heie reawe on hwete cumb.
On cinninces dic anlang standene to molenhame.
Anlang weies on winterburne ford anlang streames eft on elmere.
